**_\* Sorry For The Audio Issues! Quality should return next week!_**  
Our Ani-MAY month continues! In this action-packed episode, the guys dissect the animated film “Avengers Confidential: Black Widow & Punisher.” Vigilante Punisher and S.H.I.E.L.D. agent Black Widow reluctantly team up to stop global terrorists LEVIATHAN, but can Frank Castle be trusted? Does Widow have ulterior motives? Can ANYONE BELIEVE NICK FURY? Explosive showdowns, espionage, and unexpected alliances await so tune in now to unmask the shadows behind this thrilling Marvel anime film!

Please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us wherever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by **ComicBook Clique**, the only stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.  

Send us feedback at **ComicBookClique@Gmail.com!** You Are Worthy! 

